<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>회원가입 - 프로필 이미지</title>
  <style>
    body { text-align: center; font-family: Arial; margin-top: 100px; }
    .container { width: 300px; margin: auto; }
    img { width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid #ccc; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    input[type="file"] { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    button { padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #333; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>회원가입</h2>
    <p>프로필 이미지를 설정하세요!</p>
    <form action="/register/uploadProfile" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <input type="file" name="profile_image" accept="image/*" required><br>
      <button type="submit">회원가입하기</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>